{"tid":299307,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"電車九巴首合作推轉乘優惠","createTime":"2017-06-27T03:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T05:58:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3d538576b49010ab125effabcf6e0195f20bcb8","tid":299307,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:27:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20070084&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20070084%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170627&d=%2BU4DPnDw0U%2F5gYyF12vnWUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=f1b01e55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20070084%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170627&h=d4e3ca59\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20070084&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170627</a><br />\n<br />\n電車九巴首合作推轉乘優惠<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】九巴和電車公司本周六（7月1日）起將開展為期6個月轉乘優惠計劃，未來半年乘搭指定九巴過海路線到港島，限時內可享免費轉乘電車優惠，從港島出發先乘電車再轉搭有關過海路線到九龍、新界，同樣獲扣減電車車資；這是兩家公共交通營辦商首次合作，會視乎計劃使用情況，考慮是否延長優惠。<br />\n24條指定九巴獨營過海路線，目的地包含九龍、新界，乘客使用同一張八達通，乘搭指定路線到港島後，以拍卡起計180分鐘內可免費轉乘電車；乘搭電車後60分鐘內轉乘有關過海路線，同樣可獲扣減電車車資。<br />\n不過，已受惠於政府的長者及合資格殘疾人士「2元乘車」優惠的乘客，轉乘優惠並不適用。轉乘第二程前，不可用同一張八達通卡繳付其他巴士路線或交通工具車資，亦不能有9次以上購物等交易記錄，否則優惠會失效。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n九巴和電車互相變裝，有電車被粉飾成金色九巴模樣。<br />\n<br />\n下月取消九巴212號線<br />\n<br />\n電車公司總經理敖思灝表示，計劃透過結合電車和九巴的行車網絡，為市民帶來實惠便捷的乘車體驗。九巴企業策劃及業務發展總經理蘇偉基說，會視計劃使用情況，考慮是否延長優惠。<br />\n另外，受港鐵觀塘延線通車影響，黃埔巴士線乘客量大跌，運輸署決定同日（7月1日）起取消九巴212號線。運輸署在延線通車後，已建議取消212號線，惟區議會反對，指不少長者需搭212號線來往廣華醫院及伊利沙伯醫院。<br />\n運輸署近日去信區議會，指212號線繁忙時間平均乘客量只得19.5%，故決定取消。九巴會增加兩項巴士轉乘，包括18號線轉乘7號線來往廣華醫院，及18號線轉乘2E線來往伊利沙伯醫院。<br />\n■記者馬志剛、麥志榮<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=%2BU4DPnDw0U%2F5gYyF12vnWUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=468c187f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼"},{"pid":"08b90befb8be24b1c313975f4267a4bb8bcc9413","tid":299307,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170627/large/27la4p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F27la4p2.jpg&h=dad37d32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九巴和電車互相變裝，有電車被粉飾成金色九巴模樣。"},{"pid":"f06825caaa81f366788f0c8df8701acc9abd016e","tid":299307,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170627/large/a0405a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170627%2Flarge%2Fa0405a.gif&h=c6dbcde4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eaa392e5468a7168523f98125b882dfce975afa3","tid":299307,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:31:01.000Z","msg":"不包括中、西九龍乘客（全為聯營隧巴線）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ad584ea440fb7040b51d3d750fae043fc5b182","tid":299307,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:31:39.000Z","msg":"元朗西有份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff28ebb711ed84ba72793ca850fa22cbf47aaff5","tid":299307,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:23:24.000Z","msg":"主力都係sell西隧客去西環/銅鑼灣<br />\n上水客搭火車出紅磡再轉好過"},{"pid":"5dbdf48b62bfb44e03a483bb46b0e3b369c09ac7","tid":299307,"uid":79382,"like"